  "english": [
    "<b>Seize</b> the opportunity <b>and</b> quickly <b>recite a blessing</b> over the cup of blessing for the Grace after Meals. <b>And similarly, Rav Huna said to his son, Rabba: Seize</b> the opportunity <b>and recite a blessing.</b>",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>Is this to say that one who recites a blessing is preferable</b> to one who answers amen? <b>But isn’t it taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i> that <b>Rabbi Yosei says: The one who answers amen is greater than the one who recites the blessing? And Rabbi Nehorai said to him: By Heavens, it is so. Know</b> that this is true, <b>as the military assistants [<i>gulyarim</i>]</b> descend to the battlefield and <b>initiate the war and the mighty</b> follow them and <b>prevail.</b> The amen that follows a blessing is compared to the mighty who join the war after the assistants, illustrating that answering amen is more significant than reciting the initial blessing.",
    "The Gemara responds: This <b>is</b> a dispute between <b><i>tanna’im</i>, as it is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i>: <b>Both the one who recites a blessing and the one who answers amen are included</b> among those who “stand up and bless” (Nehemiah 9:5), <b>but one hurries to first</b> reward <b>the one who recites the blessing.</b> This <i>baraita</i> apparently holds that reciting the blessing is greater than answering amen.",
    "<b>Rabbi Elazar said</b> that <b>Rabbi Ḥanina said: Torah scholars increase peace in the world, as it is stated: “And all your children [<i>banayikh</i>] shall be taught of the Lord, and great shall be the peace of your children”</b> (Isaiah 54:13). The Sages interpreted this verse homiletically: Do not read it as: “Your children [<i>banayikh</i>],” but as: Your builders [<i>bonayikh</i>]. Torah scholars are those who build peace for their generation."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>חֲטוֹף וּבָרֵיךְ. וְכֵן אֲמַר לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Huna I, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"895\" data-full-name=\"Rav Huna I\" data-name-he=\"רב הונא\">רַב הוּנָא</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-unknown\" data-sage-type=\"unknown\" title=\"Rav Huna\" data-authority-id=\"21402\" data-full-name=\"Rav Huna\" data-name-he=\"רבה בריה\">לְרַבָּה בְּרֵיהּ</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חֲטוֹף וּבָרֵיךְ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לְמֵימְרָא דִּמְבָרֵךְ עֲדִיף? וְהָתַנְיָא,",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yosei, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yosei\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">רַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> אוֹמֵר: גָּדוֹל הָעוֹנֶה ״אָמֵן״ יוֹתֵר מִן",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַמְבָרֵךְ. וְאָמַר לוֹ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Nehorai I, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2231\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Nehorai I\" data-name-he=\"רבי נהוראי\">רַבִּי נְהוֹרַאי</span>: הַשָּׁמַיִם! כָּךְ הוּא:",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "תֵּדַע שֶׁהֲרֵי גּוּלְיָירִים מִתְגָּרִין בַּמִּלְחָמָה, וְגִבּוֹרִים נוֹצְחִין. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תַּנָּאֵי הִיא, דְּתַנְיָא:",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "אֶחָד הַמְבָרֵךְ וְאֶחָד הָעוֹנֶה ״אָמֵן״ בַּמַּשְׁמָע, אֶלָּא שֶׁמְּמַהֲרִין לַמְבָרֵךְ תְּחִילָּה.",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Pedat, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"467\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Pedat\" data-name-he=\"רַבִּי אֶלְעָזָר בֶּן פְּדָת\">רַבִּי אֶלְעָזָר</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Ḥanina bar Ḥama II, first-generation I Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1212\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Ḥanina bar Ḥama II\" data-name-he=\"רבי חנינא בר חמא\">רַבִּי חֲנִינָא</span>: תַּלְמִידֵי חֲכָמִים מַרְבִּים שָׁלוֹם בָּעוֹלָם, שֶׁנֶּאֱמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "״וְכׇל בָּנַיִךְ לִמּוּדֵי ה׳ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav said, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2749\" data-full-name=\"Rav said\" data-name-he=\"רב שלום\">וְרַב שְׁלוֹם</span> בָּנָיִךְ״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><br><br><big><strong>הַדְרָן עֲלָךְ הַגּוֹיִם אֵין לָהֶם נְזִירוּת וּסְלִיקָא לַהּ מַסֶּכֶת נָזִיר</strong></big><br><br>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">גמ&#x27;</span> חֲטוֹף</b> חטוף כוס של ברכה ובריך ברכת זימון שתהא מקיים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לברך על הכוס ברכת זימון: <b>הַשָּׁמַיִם! כָּךְ הוּא.</b> בשבועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "על שם וירם ימינו אֶל־הַשָּׁמַ֔יִם וַיִּשָּׁבַ֖ע בְּחֵ֣י הָעוֹלָ֑ם (<a href=\"https://www.sefaria.org/Daniel.12.7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-sefaria-ref=\"Daniel.12.7\">דניאל י״ב:ז׳</a>) כך הוא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שהעונה אמן גדול מן המברך: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ותדע</span>.</b> שהוא כך: <b>שהרי</b> <b>גוליירין.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "חלשין מתגרין במלחמה תחלה ואחר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כך גבורים באין ונוצחין אף כאן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "העונה אמן בא לאחר המברך ומנצח",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לומר שהעונה אמן משובח מן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "המברך: <b>תַּנָּאֵי הִיא.</b> דאיכא למ\"ד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דעונה אמן משובח מן המברך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ואית דאמר שהמברך משובח: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">א&#x27;</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">העונה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ואחד</span> הַמְבָרֵךְ בַּמַּשְׁמָע.</b> דקרא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שנאמר (תהילים ל״ד:ד׳) גדלו לה' אתי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ברכה ונרוממה שמו יחדיו אמן:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>אֶלָּא שֶׁמְּמַהֲרִין לַמְבָרֵךְ תְּחִילָּה.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ליתן שכר:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 66b:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    }
  ],
  "tosafot": [
    {
